(120,'\0','/tqj7NKj11keFuLzPsBDMUq2dOUO.jpg',93000000,'http://www.lordoftherings.net/','tt0120737','en','The Lord of the Rings: The Fellowship of the Ring','Young hobbit Frodo Baggins, after inheriting a mysterious ring from his uncle Bilbo, must leave his home in order to keep it from falling into the hands of its evil creator. Along the way, a fellowship is formed to protect the ringbearer and make sure that the ring arrives at its final destination: Mt. Doom, the only place where it can be destroyed.',78.175,'/6oom5QYQ2yQTMJIbnvbkBL9cHo6.jpg','2001-12-18',871368364,179,'Released','One ring to rule them all','The Lord of the Rings: The Fellowship of the Ring','\0'),
(121,'\0','/kWYfW2Re0rUDE6IHhy4CRuKWeFr.jpg',79000000,'http://www.lordoftherings.net/','tt0167261','en','The Lord of the Rings: The Two Towers','Frodo and Sam are trekking to Mordor to destroy the One Ring of Power while Gimli, Legolas and Aragorn search for the orc-captured Merry and Pippin. All along, nefarious wizard Saruman awaits the Fellowship members at the Orthanc Tower in Isengard.',68.157,'/5VTN0pR8gcqV3EPUHHfMGnJYN9L.jpg','2002-12-18',926287400,179,'Released','A New Power Is Rising.','The Lord of the Rings: The Two Towers','\0'),
(122,'\0','/2u7zbn8EudG6kLlBzUYqP8RyFU4.jpg',94000000,'http://www.lordoftherings.net','tt0167260','en','The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King','Aragorn is revealed as the heir to the ancient kings as he, Gandalf and the other members of the broken fellowship struggle to save Gondor from Sauron\'s forces. Meanwhile, Frodo and Sam take the ring closer to the heart of Mordor, the dark lord\'s realm.',67.311,'/rCzpDGLbOoPwLjy3OAm5NUPOTrC.jpg','2003-12-01',1118888979,201,'Released','The eye of the enemy is moving.','The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King','\0'),
(128,'\0','/mpNd0rTVrp6vHJ9Je7wSa3zC8JS.jpg',26500000,'','tt0119698','ja','もののけ姫','Ashitaka, a prince of the disappearing Emishi people, is cursed by a demonized boar god and must journey to the west to find a cure. Along the way, he encounters San, a young human woman fighting to protect the forest, and Lady Eboshi, who is trying to destroy it. Ashitaka must find a way to bring balance to this conflict.',40.616,'/cMYCDADoLKLbB83g4WnJegaZimC.jpg','1997-07-12',159414369,134,'Released','The Fate Of The World Rests On The Courage Of One Warrior.','Princess Mononoke','\0'),
