(12834,'\0','Barry Robert Pepper is a Canadian actor. He is best known for roles such as Private Daniel Jackson in Saving Private Ryan, Sergeant Michael Strank in Flags of Our Fathers, Dean Stanton in The Green Mile, Roger Maris in 61*, \"Lucky\" Ned Pepper in True Grit and Jonnie Goodboy Tyler in Battlefield Earth. He has been nominated for three Screen Actors Guild Awards and a Golden Globe Award. In 2011, for his role as Robert F. Kennedy in the miniseries The Kennedys, Pepper won the Emmy Award for Outstanding Lead Actor in a Miniseries or a Movie.','1970-04-04',2,'http://www.barrypepper.com','nm0001608','Acting','Barry Pepper','Cambell River, British Columbia, Canada',16.858,'/pmdNUqrpsoozh7QYqUgEgZQ69cA.jpg'),
